content: A photo from a walk on 2025-03-16.

photos.alt: A photo of a few thin tree branches with white flowers and tiny green leaf spurts on them. There are a pair of branches in focus in the foreground, and many more going blurry in the background. Further in the background, the forest is visible, with yellow fallen leaves, and a few larger trees. The scene is warm with a bit of a gentle sunlight.
